                                                     Perth potpourri

   
	Perth has hosted 34 Tests of which Australia have won 20, lost seven and drawn seven mdash; a winning percentage of 58.82. India have a dismal record at the Waca, having lost both Tests they have played at this venue.
 
	Following are the highlights of Tests in Perth:
 
	First Test: Aus vs Eng, 1970-71 (Match drawn)
 
